{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm going to talk\nabout a failure of intuition"},{"time":3240,"text":"that many of us suffer from."},{"time":5480,"text":"It's really a failure\nto detect a certain kind of danger."},{"time":9360,"text":"I'm going to describe a scenario"},{"time":11120,"text":"that I think is both terrifying"},{"time":14400,"text":"and likely to occur,"},{"time":16840,"text":"and that's not a good combination,"},{"time":18520,"text":"as it turns out."},{"time":20080,"text":"And yet rather than be scared,\nmost of you will feel"},{"time":22560,"text":"that what I'm talking about\nis kind of cool."}]},{"cues":[{"time":25200,"text":"I'm going to describe\nhow the gains we make"},{"time":28200,"text":"in artificial intelligence"},{"time":30000,"text":"could ultimately destroy us."},{"time":31800,"text":"And in fact, I think it's very difficult\nto see how they won't destroy us"},{"time":35280,"text":"or inspire us to destroy ourselves."},{"time":37400,"text":"And yet if you're anything like me,"},{"time":39280,"text":"you'll find that it's fun\nto think about these things."},{"time":41960,"text":"And that response is part of the problem."},{"time":45360,"text":"OK? That response should worry you."},{"time":47920,"text":"And if I were to convince you in this talk"},{"time":50600,"text":"that we were likely\nto suffer a global famine,"},{"time":54040,"text":"either because of climate change\nor some other catastrophe,"},{"time":57120,"text":"and that your grandchildren,\nor their grandchildren,"},{"time":60560,"text":"are very likely to live like this,"},{"time":63200,"text":"you wouldn't think,"},{"time":65440,"text":"\"Interesting."},{"time":66800,"text":"I like this TED Talk.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":69200,"text":"Famine isn't fun."},{"time":71800,"text":"Death by science fiction,\non the other hand, is fun,"},{"time":75200,"text":"and one of the things that worries me most\nabout the development of AI at this point"},{"time":79200,"text":"is that we seem unable to marshal\nan appropriate emotional response"},{"time":83320,"text":"to the dangers that lie ahead."},{"time":85160,"text":"I am unable to marshal this response,\nand I'm giving this talk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":90120,"text":"It's as though we stand before two doors."},{"time":92840,"text":"Behind door number one,"},{"time":94120,"text":"we stop making progress\nin building intelligent machines."},{"time":97440,"text":"Our computer hardware and software\njust stops getting better for some reason."},{"time":101480,"text":"Now take a moment\nto consider why this might happen."},{"time":105080,"text":"I mean, given how valuable\nintelligence and automation are,"},{"time":108760,"text":"we will continue to improve our technology\nif we are at all able to."},{"time":113200,"text":"What could stop us from doing this?"},{"time":115800,"text":"A full-scale nuclear war?"},{"time":119000,"text":"A global pandemic?"},{"time":122320,"text":"An asteroid impact?"},{"time":125640,"text":"Justin Bieber becoming\npresident of the United States?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":128240,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":132760,"text":"The point is, something would have to\ndestroy civilization as we know it."},{"time":137360,"text":"You have to imagine\nhow bad it would have to be"},{"time":141680,"text":"to prevent us from making\nimprovements in our technology"},{"time":145040,"text":"permanently,"},{"time":146280,"text":"generation after generation."},{"time":148320,"text":"Almost by definition,\nthis is the worst thing"},{"time":150480,"text":"that's ever happened in human history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":152520,"text":"So the only alternative,"},{"time":153840,"text":"and this is what lies\nbehind door number two,"},{"time":156200,"text":"is that we continue\nto improve our intelligent machines"},{"time":159360,"text":"year after year after year."},{"time":161720,"text":"At a certain point, we will build\nmachines that are smarter than we are,"},{"time":166080,"text":"and once we have machines\nthat are smarter than we are,"},{"time":168720,"text":"they will begin to improve themselves."},{"time":170720,"text":"And then we risk what\nthe mathematician IJ Good called"},{"time":173480,"text":"an \"intelligence explosion,\""},{"time":175280,"text":"that the process could get away from us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":178120,"text":"Now, this is often caricatured,\nas I have here,"},{"time":180960,"text":"as a fear that armies of malicious robots"},{"time":184200,"text":"will attack us."},{"time":185480,"text":"But that isn't the most likely scenario."},{"time":188200,"text":"It's not that our machines\nwill become spontaneously malevolent."},{"time":193080,"text":"The concern is really\nthat we will build machines"},{"time":195720,"text":"that are so much\nmore competent than we are"},{"time":197800,"text":"that the slightest divergence\nbetween their goals and our own"},{"time":201600,"text":"could destroy us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203960,"text":"Just think about how we relate to ants."},{"time":206600,"text":"We don't hate them."},{"time":208280,"text":"We don't go out of our way to harm them."},{"time":210360,"text":"In fact, sometimes\nwe take pains not to harm them."},{"time":212760,"text":"We step over them on the sidewalk."},{"time":214800,"text":"But whenever their presence"},{"time":216960,"text":"seriously conflicts with one of our goals,"},{"time":219480,"text":"let's say when constructing\na building like this one,"},{"time":221981,"text":"we annihilate them without a qualm."},{"time":224480,"text":"The concern is that we will\none day build machines"},{"time":227440,"text":"that, whether they're conscious or not,"},{"time":230200,"text":"could treat us with similar disregard."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233760,"text":"Now, I suspect this seems\nfar-fetched to many of you."},{"time":237360,"text":"I bet there are those of you who doubt\nthat superintelligent AI is possible,"},{"time":243720,"text":"much less inevitable."},{"time":245400,"text":"But then you must find something wrong\nwith one of the following assumptions."},{"time":249044,"text":"And there are only three of them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":251800,"text":"Intelligence is a matter of information\nprocessing in physical systems."},{"time":257320,"text":"Actually, this is a little bit more\nthan an assumption."},{"time":259959,"text":"We have already built\nnarrow intelligence into our machines,"},{"time":263440,"text":"and many of these machines perform"},{"time":265480,"text":"at a level of superhuman\nintelligence already."},{"time":268840,"text":"And we know that mere matter"},{"time":271440,"text":"can give rise to what is called\n\"general intelligence,\""},{"time":274080,"text":"an ability to think flexibly\nacross multiple domains,"},{"time":277760,"text":"because our brains have managed it. Right?"},{"time":280920,"text":"I mean, there's just atoms in here,"},{"time":284880,"text":"and as long as we continue\nto build systems of atoms"},{"time":289400,"text":"that display more and more\nintelligent behavior,"},{"time":292120,"text":"we will eventually,\nunless we are interrupted,"},{"time":294680,"text":"we will eventually\nbuild general intelligence"},{"time":298080,"text":"into our machines."}]},{"cues":[{"time":299400,"text":"It's crucial to realize\nthat the rate of progress doesn't matter,"},{"time":303080,"text":"because any progress\nis enough to get us into the end zone."},{"time":306280,"text":"We don't need Moore's law to continue.\nWe don't need exponential progress."},{"time":310080,"text":"We just need to keep going."}]},{"cues":[{"time":313480,"text":"The second assumption\nis that we will keep going."},{"time":317000,"text":"We will continue to improve\nour intelligent machines."},{"time":321000,"text":"And given the value of intelligence --"},{"time":325400,"text":"I mean, intelligence is either\nthe source of everything we value"},{"time":328960,"text":"or we need it to safeguard\neverything we value."},{"time":331760,"text":"It is our most valuable resource."},{"time":334040,"text":"So we want to do this."},{"time":335600,"text":"We have problems\nthat we desperately need to solve."},{"time":338960,"text":"We want to cure diseases\nlike Alzheimer's and cancer."},{"time":342960,"text":"We want to understand economic systems.\nWe want to improve our climate science."},{"time":346920,"text":"So we will do this, if we can."},{"time":349200,"text":"The train is already out of the station,\nand there's no brake to pull."}]},{"cues":[{"time":353880,"text":"Finally, we don't stand\non a peak of intelligence,"},{"time":359360,"text":"or anywhere near it, likely."},{"time":361640,"text":"And this really is the crucial insight."},{"time":363560,"text":"This is what makes\nour situation so precarious,"},{"time":366000,"text":"and this is what makes our intuitions\nabout risk so unreliable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":371120,"text":"Now, just consider the smartest person\nwho has ever lived."},{"time":374640,"text":"On almost everyone's shortlist here\nis John von Neumann."},{"time":378080,"text":"I mean, the impression that von Neumann\nmade on the people around him,"},{"time":381440,"text":"and this included the greatest\nmathematicians and physicists of his time,"},{"time":385520,"text":"is fairly well-documented."},{"time":387480,"text":"If only half the stories\nabout him are half true,"},{"time":391280,"text":"there's no question"},{"time":392520,"text":"he's one of the smartest people\nwho has ever lived."},{"time":395000,"text":"So consider the spectrum of intelligence."},{"time":398320,"text":"Here we have John von Neumann."},{"time":401560,"text":"And then we have you and me."},{"time":404120,"text":"And then we have a chicken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405440,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":407400,"text":"Sorry, a chicken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":408640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":409920,"text":"There's no reason for me to make this talk\nmore depressing than it needs to be."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413680,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":416339,"text":"It seems overwhelmingly likely, however,\nthat the spectrum of intelligence"},{"time":419840,"text":"extends much further\nthan we currently conceive,"},{"time":423880,"text":"and if we build machines\nthat are more intelligent than we are,"},{"time":427120,"text":"they will very likely\nexplore this spectrum"},{"time":429440,"text":"in ways that we can't imagine,"},{"time":431320,"text":"and exceed us in ways\nthat we can't imagine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435000,"text":"And it's important to recognize that\nthis is true by virtue of speed alone."},{"time":439360,"text":"Right? So imagine if we just built\na superintelligent AI"},{"time":444440,"text":"that was no smarter\nthan your average team of researchers"},{"time":447920,"text":"at Stanford or MIT."},{"time":450240,"text":"Well, electronic circuits\nfunction about a million times faster"},{"time":453240,"text":"than biochemical ones,"},{"time":454520,"text":"so this machine should think\nabout a million times faster"},{"time":457680,"text":"than the minds that built it."},{"time":459520,"text":"So you set it running for a week,"},{"time":461200,"text":"and it will perform 20,000 years\nof human-level intellectual work,"},{"time":466400,"text":"week after week after week."},{"time":469640,"text":"How could we even understand,\nmuch less constrain,"},{"time":472760,"text":"a mind making this sort of progress?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":476840,"text":"The other thing that's worrying, frankly,"},{"time":479000,"text":"is that, imagine the best case scenario."},{"time":484000,"text":"So imagine we hit upon a design\nof superintelligent AI"},{"time":488200,"text":"that has no safety concerns."},{"time":489600,"text":"We have the perfect design\nthe first time around."},{"time":492880,"text":"It's as though we've been handed an oracle"},{"time":495120,"text":"that behaves exactly as intended."},{"time":497160,"text":"Well, this machine would be\nthe perfect labor-saving device."},{"time":501680,"text":"It can design the machine\nthat can build the machine"},{"time":504133,"text":"that can do any physical work,"},{"time":505920,"text":"powered by sunlight,"},{"time":507400,"text":"more or less for the cost\nof raw materials."},{"time":510120,"text":"So we're talking about\nthe end of human drudgery."},{"time":513400,"text":"We're also talking about the end\nof most intellectual work."}]},{"cues":[{"time":517200,"text":"So what would apes like ourselves\ndo in this circumstance?"},{"time":520280,"text":"Well, we'd be free to play Frisbee\nand give each other massages."},{"time":525840,"text":"Add some LSD and some\nquestionable wardrobe choices,"},{"time":528720,"text":"and the whole world\ncould be like Burning Man."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530920,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534320,"text":"Now, that might sound pretty good,"},{"time":537280,"text":"but ask yourself what would happen"},{"time":539680,"text":"under our current economic\nand political order?"},{"time":542440,"text":"It seems likely that we would witness"},{"time":544880,"text":"a level of wealth inequality\nand unemployment"},{"time":549040,"text":"that we have never seen before."},{"time":550560,"text":"Absent a willingness\nto immediately put this new wealth"},{"time":553200,"text":"to the service of all humanity,"},{"time":555640,"text":"a few trillionaires could grace\nthe covers of our business magazines"},{"time":559280,"text":"while the rest of the world\nwould be free to starve."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562320,"text":"And what would the Russians\nor the Chinese do"},{"time":564640,"text":"if they heard that some company\nin Silicon Valley"},{"time":567280,"text":"was about to deploy a superintelligent AI?"},{"time":570040,"text":"This machine would be capable\nof waging war,"},{"time":572920,"text":"whether terrestrial or cyber,"},{"time":575160,"text":"with unprecedented power."},{"time":578120,"text":"This is a winner-take-all scenario."},{"time":580000,"text":"To be six months ahead\nof the competition here"},{"time":583160,"text":"is to be 500,000 years ahead,"},{"time":585960,"text":"at a minimum."},{"time":587480,"text":"So it seems that even mere rumors\nof this kind of breakthrough"},{"time":592240,"text":"could cause our species to go berserk."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594640,"text":"Now, one of the most frightening things,"},{"time":597560,"text":"in my view, at this moment,"},{"time":600360,"text":"are the kinds of things\nthat AI researchers say"},{"time":604680,"text":"when they want to be reassuring."},{"time":607000,"text":"And the most common reason\nwe're told not to worry is time."},{"time":610480,"text":"This is all a long way off,\ndon't you know."},{"time":612560,"text":"This is probably 50 or 100 years away."},{"time":615720,"text":"One researcher has said,"},{"time":617000,"text":"\"Worrying about AI safety"},{"time":618600,"text":"is like worrying\nabout overpopulation on Mars.\""},{"time":622116,"text":"This is the Silicon Valley version"},{"time":623760,"text":"of \"don't worry your\npretty little head about it.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":626160,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":627520,"text":"No one seems to notice"},{"time":629440,"text":"that referencing the time horizon"},{"time":632080,"text":"is a total non sequitur."},{"time":634680,"text":"If intelligence is just a matter\nof information processing,"},{"time":637960,"text":"and we continue to improve our machines,"},{"time":640640,"text":"we will produce\nsome form of superintelligence."},{"time":644320,"text":"And we have no idea\nhow long it will take us"},{"time":648000,"text":"to create the conditions\nto do that safely."},{"time":652200,"text":"Let me say that again."},{"time":653520,"text":"We have no idea how long it will take us"},{"time":657360,"text":"to create the conditions\nto do that safely."}]},{"cues":[{"time":660920,"text":"And if you haven't noticed,\n50 years is not what it used to be."},{"time":664400,"text":"This is 50 years in months."},{"time":666880,"text":"This is how long we've had the iPhone."},{"time":669440,"text":"This is how long \"The Simpsons\"\nhas been on television."},{"time":672680,"text":"Fifty years is not that much time"},{"time":675080,"text":"to meet one of the greatest challenges\nour species will ever face."},{"time":679640,"text":"Once again, we seem to be failing\nto have an appropriate emotional response"},{"time":683680,"text":"to what we have every reason\nto believe is coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":686400,"text":"The computer scientist Stuart Russell\nhas a nice analogy here."},{"time":690400,"text":"He said, imagine that we received\na message from an alien civilization,"},{"time":695320,"text":"which read:"},{"time":697040,"text":"\"People of Earth,"},{"time":698600,"text":"we will arrive on your planet in 50 years."},{"time":701800,"text":"Get ready.\""},{"time":703400,"text":"And now we're just counting down\nthe months until the mothership lands?"},{"time":707680,"text":"We would feel a little\nmore urgency than we do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":712680,"text":"Another reason we're told not to worry"},{"time":714560,"text":"is that these machines\ncan't help but share our values"},{"time":717600,"text":"because they will be literally\nextensions of ourselves."},{"time":720240,"text":"They'll be grafted onto our brains,"},{"time":722080,"text":"and we'll essentially\nbecome their limbic systems."},{"time":725120,"text":"Now take a moment to consider"},{"time":726560,"text":"that the safest\nand only prudent path forward,"},{"time":729760,"text":"recommended,"},{"time":731120,"text":"is to implant this technology\ndirectly into our brains."},{"time":734600,"text":"Now, this may in fact be the safest\nand only prudent path forward,"},{"time":738000,"text":"but usually one's safety concerns\nabout a technology"},{"time":741080,"text":"have to be pretty much worked out\nbefore you stick it inside your head."}]},{"cues":[{"time":744760,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":746800,"text":"The deeper problem is that\nbuilding superintelligent AI on its own"},{"time":752160,"text":"seems likely to be easier"},{"time":753920,"text":"than building superintelligent AI"},{"time":755800,"text":"and having the completed neuroscience"},{"time":757600,"text":"that allows us to seamlessly\nintegrate our minds with it."},{"time":760800,"text":"And given that the companies\nand governments doing this work"},{"time":764000,"text":"are likely to perceive themselves\nas being in a race against all others,"},{"time":767680,"text":"given that to win this race\nis to win the world,"},{"time":770960,"text":"provided you don't destroy it\nin the next moment,"},{"time":773440,"text":"then it seems likely\nthat whatever is easier to do"},{"time":776080,"text":"will get done first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778560,"text":"Now, unfortunately,\nI don't have a solution to this problem,"},{"time":781440,"text":"apart from recommending\nthat more of us think about it."},{"time":784080,"text":"I think we need something\nlike a Manhattan Project"},{"time":786480,"text":"on the topic of artificial intelligence."},{"time":788520,"text":"Not to build it, because I think\nwe'll inevitably do that,"},{"time":791280,"text":"but to understand\nhow to avoid an arms race"},{"time":794640,"text":"and to build it in a way\nthat is aligned with our interests."},{"time":798160,"text":"When you're talking\nabout superintelligent AI"},{"time":800320,"text":"that can make changes to itself,"},{"time":802600,"text":"it seems that we only have one chance\nto get the initial conditions right,"},{"time":807240,"text":"and even then we will need to absorb"},{"time":809320,"text":"the economic and political\nconsequences of getting them right."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813760,"text":"But the moment we admit"},{"time":815840,"text":"that information processing\nis the source of intelligence,"},{"time":820720,"text":"that some appropriate computational system\nis what the basis of intelligence is,"},{"time":826360,"text":"and we admit that we will improve\nthese systems continuously,"},{"time":831280,"text":"and we admit that the horizon\nof cognition very likely far exceeds"},{"time":835760,"text":"what we currently know,"},{"time":838120,"text":"then we have to admit"},{"time":839360,"text":"that we are in the process\nof building some sort of god."},{"time":843400,"text":"Now would be a good time"},{"time":845000,"text":"to make sure it's a god we can live with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":848120,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":849680,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}